    • AlarmInstance

      public AlarmInstance()
      Default constructor. Note that this does not initialize fields to their default values from the schema. If that is desired then one should use newBuilder().

    • AlarmInstance

      public AlarmInstance(String alarmclass, String device, Object source, List<String> location, String maskedby, String screencommand)
      All-args constructor.
      Parameters:
      alarmclass - The alarm class; provides inheritable shared values
      device - The name of the associated device
      source - Provides source specific information via a union.
      location - The locations associated with the alarm
      maskedby - The name of the parent alarm, which if active, masks this alarm (flood suppression via logical hierarchy)
      screencommand - The command to open the related control system screen
